Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,--------main--------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.83,0:00:39.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,留意到她也乘同一辆电车
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.52,0:00:41.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是第二学期开学时的事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.33,0:00:50.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首班前往学园前的列车马上要发车了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.39,0:00:53.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关门请注意
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.50,0:00:53.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}等等
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.20,0:01:11.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于她
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.69,0:01:13.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只知道她是邻班的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.44,0:01:17.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像很喜欢看书  经常在往返的电车上看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.95,0:01:24.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然这只是每天乘同一辆电车时的一点点小小的发现而已
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.66,0:01:27.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从那时起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.32,0:01:31.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我开始在意起她的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.31,0:01:33.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.37,0:01:38.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但别说详细地四处调查了  连招呼都没打过
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.02,0:01:46.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仅仅是能在远处注视着她  桂言叶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.85,0:01:51.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就觉得  那一整天过得充实多了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.17,0:01:58.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道吗  手机的恋爱魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.13,0:01:58.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.94,0:02:01.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把喜欢的人的照片当作待机图片保持3个星期
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.18,0:02:05.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有让任何人发现的话  恋爱就能成功
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.85,0:02:38.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有让任何人发现的话  恋爱就能成功吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.38,0:02:44.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真荒唐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.16,0:02:51.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  在看什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.27,0:02:54.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈  就是那个恋爱的魔法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.43,0:02:57.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊藤对流行还真敏感呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.62,0:03:00.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是这样的  而且跟西园寺没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.90,0:03:02.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真冷淡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.40,0:03:03.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然之间干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.62,0:03:08.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从今天起是同桌了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.32,0:03:10.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请多多关照了  伊藤诚同学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.20,0:03:12.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.29,0:03:13.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真冷淡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.63,0:03:14.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.33,0:03:17.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊藤好像学习很好的样子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.02,0:03:18.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一般般
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.11,0:03:20.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真冷淡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.77,0:03:22.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  我说伊藤
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.84,0:03:23.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.97,0:03:26.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢四班的桂同学啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.54,0:03:28.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看到了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.78,0:03:31.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼哼  看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.22,0:03:40.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  西园寺  喂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.79,0:03:41.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在上课呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.31,0:03:44.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这件事绝对不要跟别人说哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.23,0:03:46.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.12,0:03:47.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.51,0:03:49.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么问题
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.28,0:03:49.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.80,0:03:55.78,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz28}{\pos(352,300)}这就是那个魔法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.39,0:03:59.80,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,300)}不是！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.11,0:04:02.29,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz28}{\pos(352,250)}那为什么会有她的照片？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.42,0:04:04.80,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz15}{\pos(352,300)}碰巧拍到的！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.21,0:04:06.80,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz28}{\pos(252,70)}这种理由谁会信啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.38,0:04:10.54,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz21}{\pos(172,290)}是啊  我也不信
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.54,0:04:11.80,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz28}{\pos(482,220)}哈哈哈…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.18,0:04:16.30,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz28}{\pos(302,320)}她是四班的桂同学吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.65,0:04:18.31,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz20}{\pos(302,320)}你别管了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.61,0:04:21.31,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz25}{\pos(360,300)}不用隐瞒哦  她很可爱的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.65,0:04:25.81,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz25}{\pos(302,320)}魔法进行到第几天了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.13,0:04:27.31,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz20}{\pos(302,320)}第一天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.59,0:04:28.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么快！？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.67,0:04:29.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.77,0:04:30.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.79,0:04:51.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泰介
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.91,0:04:53.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要偷懒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.57,0:04:54.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基本都弄完了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.22,0:04:59.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事随便了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.77,0:05:00.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.82,0:05:01.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诚你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.73,0:05:05.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和西园寺关系有那么好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.54,0:05:07.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是她跟我搭话的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.55,0:05:08.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有希望哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.35,0:05:12.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西园寺别看那样可是很受欢迎的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.16,0:05:16.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还以为她只是个烦人的家伙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.90,0:05:19.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你对女孩的审美观真是差啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.89,0:05:20.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用你管
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.30,0:05:24.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好啊  西园寺真可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.81,0:05:26.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么  你喜欢她吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.09,0:05:28.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可爱的女孩我都喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.16,0:05:34.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明明诚心追求  诚  你也太狡猾了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.41,0:05:38.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  我可什么都没做  和西园寺之间什么事也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.13,0:05:41.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能这么说也只是现在了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.54,0:05:45.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你马上会扔下我们  跨过成人的那道坎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.97,0:05:47.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但对方是西园寺  就…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.90,0:05:51.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自大  又是你赢  只有我的春天永远不会来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.03,0:05:54.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把你杀了后我也去死
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.18,0:05:55.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫名其妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.90,0:05:56.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊藤
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.80,0:05:59.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  有话要跟你说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.91,0:06:00.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.74,0:06:02.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这可不能说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.27,0:06:03.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你别开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.97,0:06:07.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋  你绝对是误解了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.89,0:06:10.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是有别的人在的话  伊藤可能会觉得尴尬呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.21,0:06:13.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜毕业
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.22,0:06:13.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.25,0:06:18.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么西园寺有屋顶的钥匙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.03,0:06:21.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是天文部的部长啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.48,0:06:22.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是个一年级学生？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.90,0:06:25.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都被废部好多年了  我自称的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.32,0:06:29.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说想观测天体  很容易就批准了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.52,0:06:32.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实际上一次都没做过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.01,0:06:34.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样有意义吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.45,0:06:36.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样不觉得有趣吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.46,0:06:40.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有个秘密的地方  不觉得刺激  快乐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.97,0:06:42.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.38,0:06:46.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可我现在满是不安  不觉得快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.69,0:06:47.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要说的话是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.37,0:06:49.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.55,0:06:51.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你叫我过来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.30,0:06:54.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了  伊藤真是急性子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.10,0:06:56.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我宣布了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.90,0:07:03.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我刚才和桂同学成为朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.85,0:07:07.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,体育课不是和四班合上了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.54,0:07:08.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那时候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.10,0:07:11.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时  怎么搞到的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.13,0:07:14.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很感兴趣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.28,0:07:18.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桂同学身体很弱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.85,0:07:20.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才也是在旁听
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.90,0:07:23.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也装病  就和她一起休息了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.36,0:07:24.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,装病是不行的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.11,0:07:28.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我担心伊藤嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.44,0:07:30.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟偷看到了你的手机啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.79,0:07:36.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后聊了很多  桂同学的情况好像都了解了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.31,0:07:37.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.61,0:07:42.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为桂同学很可爱  在班上很受欢迎哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.52,0:07:43.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.84,0:07:47.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后  基本没什么朋友  很寂寞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.74,0:07:51.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我还拿到了邮件地址和电话号码  厉害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.10,0:07:52.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.34,0:07:54.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打算今晚就给她打电话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.51,0:07:57.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,具体内容之后我也会告诉伊藤的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.21,0:08:02.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是  西园寺  为什么要为我做到这个地步呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.18,0:08:06.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊藤在女孩中可是很受欢迎的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.08,0:08:07.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.98,0:08:09.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看  果然没注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.04,0:08:11.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.21,0:08:13.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果伊藤有喜欢的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.95,0:08:16.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我作为女生代表可不能装看不到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.07,0:08:20.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  伊藤生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.97,0:08:23.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是要戏弄你的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.26,0:08:28.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟谁  跟谁说了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.57,0:08:32.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊藤好吓人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.83,0:08:35.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的  再不会对谁说的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.79,0:08:37.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「再」  什么叫「再」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.20,0:08:39.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.36,0:08:42.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.38,0:08:43.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.14,0:08:48.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟谁都没说哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.03,0:08:49.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.13,0:08:50.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.58,0:08:52.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.51,0:08:54.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了就让开
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.17,0:08:59.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这让别人看见了可不妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.56,0:09:04.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  因为刚才大吃一惊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.66,0:09:07.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系  伊藤是很老实的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.84,0:09:11.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来为你加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.83,0:09:16.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可不是开玩笑  我会好好帮你一把的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.49,0:09:19.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了让伊藤的单恋能实现
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.40,0:09:25.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就交给我世界吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.74,0:09:27.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还没说同意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.71,0:09:30.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不交给我的话就说出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.53,0:09:31.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  西园寺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.04,0:09:32.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫世界就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.34,0:09:37.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西园寺世界  世界是「WORLD」的世界哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.52,0:09:41.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,规模庞大的名字吧  我很喜欢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.88,0:09:42.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太大了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.90,0:09:43.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.85,0:09:45.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  很帅气呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.39,0:09:46.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.86,0:09:52.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得我好逊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.94,0:09:54.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没这种事情哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.91,0:09:57.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才对你大声嚷嚷  真是对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.23,0:09:59.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了啦  请多多关照  诚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.30,0:10:00.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我也直呼其名吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.67,0:10:01.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.81,0:10:13.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.03,0:10:16.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刹那  在等我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.80,0:10:18.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟伊藤聊了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.27,0:10:20.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道那个了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.27,0:10:25.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么啊  伊藤很有趣  就和他做朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.37,0:10:27.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天去哪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.15,0:10:31.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甜品店有糯米团拼盘的新品了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.83,0:10:32.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  就决定去那了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.41,0:10:41.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会变成这样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.68,0:10:45.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.20,0:10:48.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  诚  现在正在进行中吗  还是刚开始…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.72,0:11:05.98,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz16}{\pos(352,255)}对她进行了些调查
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.98,0:11:07.14,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz20}{\pos(352,250)}兴趣是读书
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.14,0:11:08.66,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz-28}{\pos(252,350)}这我知道！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.66,0:11:10.66,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz-17}{\pos(152,350)}每天午饭在学生食堂\N喜欢的食物是鸡肉拉面\N偶尔吃意式实心面
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.66,0:11:12.15,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz28}{\pos(152,250)}爱吃面吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.15,0:11:14.40,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz0}{\pos(352,280)}胸部非常大
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.31,0:11:15.15,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz0}{\pos(352,150)}这我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.77,0:11:15.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,色狼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.02,0:11:18.15,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz20}{\pos(352,250)}在这里重大宣布！！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.30,0:11:18.15,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz2}{\pos(352,80)}什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.19,0:11:20.70,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,说好了今天和桂同学3个人\N一起吃午饭\N  请·多·关·照
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.22,0:11:25.70,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,说好了今天和桂同学3个人一起吃午饭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.70,0:11:27.20,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,请多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.79,0:11:29.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.96,0:11:30.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.47,0:11:33.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.35,0:11:37.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行  不行  绝对不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.27,0:11:39.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的  来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.95,0:11:42.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天到了今天怎么变成这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.56,0:11:45.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚上煲电话时说到的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.20,0:11:46.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.62,0:11:48.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是叫你吃午饭  要理由吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.65,0:11:50.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然要  我还没作好心理准备
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.02,0:11:52.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.52,0:11:54.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光是想像脚就在抖了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.89,0:11:56.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是男子汉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.16,0:11:57.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不当男子汉也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.82,0:11:59.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就成为男子汉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.45,0:12:00.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经放弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.88,0:12:02.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.24,0:12:05.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  说起来  我没做物理的报告
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.82,0:12:07.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个别去管它
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.64,0:12:08.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.85,0:12:11.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  对了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.54,0:12:14.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我问了桂同学喜欢的人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.34,0:12:16.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想知道的话就过来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.75,0:12:22.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桂同学  现在没有在交往的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.83,0:12:23.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.67,0:12:24.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的真的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.99,0:12:26.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然有在意的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.50,0:12:29.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没有到喜欢地步的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.06,0:12:30.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}有在意的人了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.72,0:12:35.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要认输  所以说  诚努力的话还是有机会的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.63,0:12:39.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}是吗  我知道这个就已经很满足了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.58,0:12:39.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  笨蛋笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.06,0:12:42.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱慕如果只是凭想像是不会实现的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.32,0:12:47.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救命啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.35,0:12:55.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.15,0:12:58.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  桂同学  让你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.44,0:12:59.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西园寺同学
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.58,0:13:02.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉抱歉  久等了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.36,0:13:05.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我也是刚刚来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.57,0:13:07.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.48,0:13:09.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.41,0:13:13.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好  初次见面  我是桂言叶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.94,0:13:16.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  我是伊藤诚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.31,0:13:18.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是在相亲吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.03,0:13:21.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  别畏畏缩缩的了  来吃午饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.76,0:13:22.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.92,0:13:23.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.86,0:13:27.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇  桂同学  这看上去很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.69,0:13:30.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然还不是很拿手  请品尝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.44,0:13:33.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真厉害  自己做的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.76,0:13:38.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  特意邀请我来  想总归要做些什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.24,0:13:40.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用那么费心的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.90,0:13:43.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  诚  桂同学亲手做的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.75,0:13:44.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.38,0:13:47.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊藤同学也是  可以的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.17,0:13:49.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然  乐意之极  我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.85,0:13:55.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.99,0:13:59.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  也不错吧…  喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.08,0:14:05.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刺激舌头的没尝过的味道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.32,0:14:08.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桂同学  难道你做菜…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.84,0:14:11.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  基本上是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.13,0:14:11.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.11,0:14:13.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.71,0:14:15.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.02,0:14:18.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是第一次尝到的味道  舌头吃了一惊而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.11,0:14:21.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好吃  很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.67,0:14:22.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好  加油
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.19,0:14:26.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是好吃到爆了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.39,0:14:29.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像接受了  结局很不错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.70,0:14:32.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就给你倒热茶  不用太急哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.81,0:14:34.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备得真充分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.96,0:14:38.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给  伊藤同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.22,0:14:41.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.00,0:14:41.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊藤同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.28,0:14:49.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一口气塞过头了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.74,0:14:51.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁叫你这么没轻重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.49,0:14:52.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.95,0:14:53.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桂同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.68,0:14:57.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  一不小心…  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.56,0:14:59.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.57,0:15:00.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要到哪里去？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.24,0:15:03.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  我去下洗手间
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.47,0:15:11.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊藤同学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.20,0:15:13.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来就要祈祷一切顺利了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.23,0:15:19.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.08,0:15:20.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.97,0:15:23.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊藤同学真是有趣的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.92,0:15:26.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道原以为我是个可怕的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.03,0:15:29.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本以为你是很冷静的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.65,0:15:33.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平时是很冷静的哟  只是今天比较特别
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.38,0:15:34.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特别吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.76,0:15:37.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  特别是指因为要和桂同学一起吃午饭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.44,0:15:38.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  不…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.23,0:15:41.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并不是说只有我们两个人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.36,0:15:45.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加上世界是三个人一起  并没有别的意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.34,0:15:48.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  世界去洗手间还真久啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.15,0:15:54.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？  就是说桂同学以前就知道我的事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.72,0:15:55.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.56,0:15:59.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是觉得从西园寺同学那里了解到的和实际感觉不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.42,0:16:00.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.57,0:16:05.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说得也是呢  可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.15,0:16:10.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但桂同学果然很可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.34,0:16:14.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  不  真的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.91,0:16:18.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我非常感谢世界
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.62,0:16:19.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.72,0:16:23.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的  能和桂同学这样聊天真是太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.25,0:16:25.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那只能算是普通
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.39,0:16:27.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诚太晚熟了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.44,0:16:29.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.83,0:16:31.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这样啦  都一个班嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.52,0:16:35.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正我觉得要是简单就成了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.71,0:16:37.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以后就没什么乐趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.84,0:16:39.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真过分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.55,0:16:43.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但若不是世界帮忙的话是绝对不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.66,0:16:44.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.86,0:16:49.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界  我打算明天向桂同学表白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.68,0:16:54.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许会被甩  但我想好好传达我现在的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.21,0:16:58.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很有男人气概哦  诚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.52,0:16:59.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.66,0:17:01.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诚的话一定能成功的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.23,0:17:02.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.16,0:17:03.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.16,0:17:04.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.32,0:17:09.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  一定要成功
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.07,0:17:21.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.91,0:17:27.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}到学园前方向的电车即将进站了  请退到待车线后等待
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.60,0:17:28.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桂同学
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.01,0:17:29.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊藤同学
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.86,0:17:33.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.41,0:17:34.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.56,0:17:37.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊藤同学也乘这辆电车呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.37,0:17:37.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.36,0:17:40.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊藤同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.46,0:17:42.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.40,0:17:46.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备  起跑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.39,0:17:48.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.39,0:17:49.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西园寺同学
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.65,0:17:51.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我身体也不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.28,0:17:59.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  西园寺同学
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.52,0:18:00.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什  什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.40,0:18:04.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊藤同学向我告白了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.56,0:18:08.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚认识就告白  真是冒失的家伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.23,0:18:11.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…接受了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.26,0:18:15.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.78,0:18:17.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.18,0:18:21.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还记得我以前说过有个在意的人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.82,0:18:23.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记得  记得
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.74,0:18:28.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在和诚约会的时候想起那个人可不行哟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.79,0:18:31.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诚很感情很细腻的  知道了一定会难过的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.10,0:18:35.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在意的那个人…就是伊藤同学
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.87,0:18:36.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.95,0:18:42.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉每天在电车里一直有人看着我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.90,0:18:45.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也告诉自己只是自作多情而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.87,0:18:49.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但一在意起来就越来越在意了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.74,0:18:51.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人就是伊藤同学
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.92,0:18:53.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.58,0:18:56.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不就是两情相愿吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.45,0:18:59.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  今天早上被伊藤同学告白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.42,0:19:01.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是真的很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.84,0:19:05.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的很感谢西园寺同学
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.11,0:19:09.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是西园寺同学介绍让我们认识的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.15,0:19:14.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不是这样的话  是绝对没机会和伊藤同学认识的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.68,0:19:18.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱慕如果只是凭想像的话  是不会实现的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.36,0:19:21.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同样的话我也告诉过诚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.07,0:19:26.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为那家伙也说过  只是远远看着桂同学就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.85,0:19:27.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.32,0:19:30.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诚其实是很善良的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.46,0:19:33.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常喜欢桂同学的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.29,0:19:37.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.31,0:19:39.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.76,0:19:47.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没在学校告白呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.43,0:19:49.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.70,0:19:54.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事  在学校大家都在很难说出口吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.22,0:19:56.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在等桂同学吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.94,0:19:57.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.87,0:20:00.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桂同学说有委员会要开所以要晚点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.51,0:20:01.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.80,0:20:03.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可别心急了做出什么越轨的事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.89,0:20:04.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.95,0:20:05.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗  是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.20,0:20:07.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,电灯泡我可不需要哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.01,0:20:10.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋  我也是坐这条线的班车
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.95,0:20:13.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人  我从没在车上看见过你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.76,0:20:15.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和诚是相反路线的车
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.71,0:20:17.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我家在横手的原坂町哟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.96,0:20:18.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.23,0:20:21.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  不是告诉过你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.70,0:20:22.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.27,0:20:23.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.32,0:20:25.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐  世界
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.99,0:20:26.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.72,0:20:28.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么帮我这么多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.57,0:20:30.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是偷看了我的电话的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.32,0:20:32.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一般是不会做到这地步的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.64,0:20:33.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为很有意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.91,0:20:34.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就只是这个？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.09,0:20:36.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以为还有什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.82,0:20:39.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有比看别人的恋爱更有趣的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.99,0:20:41.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.53,0:20:44.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,电视的演艺圈新闻和电视剧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.31,0:20:45.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基本上都是恋爱故事对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.24,0:20:46.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.45,0:20:48.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像这样二人的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.09,0:20:52.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  不是说我的名字而是指这个「WORLD」哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.56,0:20:53.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.86,0:20:56.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像这样以自己的意志来控制
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.65,0:20:59.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像明白了…又好像不明白…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.29,0:21:02.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这点很有意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.92,0:21:05.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好象欠了你一个大人情的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.55,0:21:10.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很大哟  花一辈子的时间都偿还不完的大哟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.50,0:21:11.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.59,0:21:13.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}马上开往原坂町方向的列车就要进站了  请退到黄线以后等候
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.27,0:21:13.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗你的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.12,0:21:15.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我一定会还这个情的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.13,0:21:18.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗  不用逞强哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.59,0:21:20.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算逞强也一定会还
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.94,0:21:24.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那要做点什么来回报我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.47,0:21:25.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管什么我都会做的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.81,0:21:26.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.44,0:21:29.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢慢考虑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.39,0:21:32.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看吧  电车也来了  什么时候都可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.45,0:21:46.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.53,0:21:48.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.08,0:21:55.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,约会要加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,--------ED--------
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.41,0:23:27.42,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,Scroll up;0;396;8;0,{\frz-90}君のことを想う　そのたび
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.87,0:23:33.20,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,Scroll up;0;396;9;0,{\frz-90}上手く息が出来ない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.68,0:23:39.84,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,Scroll up;0;396;9;0,{\frz-90}本当の自分を隠して
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.86,0:23:45.68,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,Scroll up;0;396;10;0,{\frz-90}何が欲しいんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.97,0:23:53.09,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,Scroll up;0;396;11;0,{\frz-90}一番の理解者なんて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.70,0:23:57.65,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,Scroll up;0;396;10;0,{\frz-90}笑顔見せるかな…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.23,0:24:05.20,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,Scroll up;0;396;10;0,{\frz-90}一つまた嘘がこぼれた
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.02,0:24:12.03,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,Scroll up;0;396;12;0,{\frz-90}君が好きなのに
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.27,0:24:15.93,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,Scroll up;0;396;11;0,{\frz-90}この声が枯れるまで
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.15,0:24:21.26,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,Scroll up;0;396;8;0,{\frz-90}言葉にしたい
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.08,0:24:23.26,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,Scroll up;0;396;9;0,{\frz-90}気付いて…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.16,0:24:34.21,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,Scroll up;0;396;15;0,{\frz-90}狭い空の下で　私は君を見つめてる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.41,0:23:27.42,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,Scroll up;0;396;9;0,{\frz-90}每当想起你的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.87,0:23:33.20,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,Scroll up;0;396;9;0,{\frz-90}我就会呼吸急促
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.68,0:23:39.84,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,Scroll up;0;396;8;0,{\frz-90}一直压抑着自己深处的内心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.86,0:23:45.68,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,Scroll up;0;396;10;0,{\frz-90}我究竟在期盼着什么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.97,0:23:53.09,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,Scroll up;0;396;10;0,{\frz-90}是想要那个最理解我的人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.70,0:23:57.65,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,Scroll up;0;396;10;0,{\frz-90}对我绽放笑容吧{\fnMS Gothic}…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.23,0:24:05.20,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,Scroll up;0;396;10;0,{\frz-90}我为什么会再次言不由衷
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.02,0:24:12.03,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,Scroll up;0;396;12;0,{\frz-90}明明是这样地爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.27,0:24:15.93,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,Scroll up;0;396;11;0,{\frz-90}这样的心声要对你重复
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.15,0:24:21.26,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,Scroll up;0;396;8;0,{\frz-90}直到声音嘶哑
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.08,0:24:23.26,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,Scroll up;0;396;9;0,{\frz-90}留意到了吗{\fnMS Gothic}…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.16,0:24:34.21,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,Scroll up;0;396;15;0,{\frz-90}在这片小小的天空下　我在守望着你
